\section{Introduction}
\section{Related Work}

% Subsections within the main sections
\subsection{Motivation}
\subsection{Background}
```

3. Add the `\tableofcontents` command after the document title but before the beginning of the main content. This will generate the TOC.

```latex
% Document title
\title{My Document}
\author{Your Name}
\date{\today}

% Add the table of contents
\maketitle
\tableofcontents

% Main content starts here
```

